<div id="reference">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row padded">
      <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
        <h2>Studio Lyon 3</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row padding-top text-center">
        <!-- <a href="{{ reference.lien_juxtapose }}" class="btn btn-primary">Lien juxtapose</a> -->
        <iframe frameborder="0" class="juxtapose" width="700" height="400" src="https://cdn.knightlab.com/libs/juxtapose/latest/embed/index.html?uid=1e9c991c-2655-11ea-b9b8-0edaf8f81e27"></iframe>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center padded">
      <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
        <h4>Avant</h4>

        <div id="carousel-avant" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel-avant" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-avant" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-avant" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/avantbardet1.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/avantbardet2.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/avantbardet3.png") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Controls -->
          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-avant" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-avant" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <h4>Après</h4>
        <div id="carousel-apres" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#carousel-apres" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-apres" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#carousel-apres" data-slide-to="2"></li>
          </ol>
          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
            <div class="item active">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/apresbardet1.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/apresbardet2.png") %>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
              <%= image_tag("/images/references/apresbardet3.png") %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Controls -->
          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-apres" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>
          <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-apres" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center">
      <a href="https://www.meilleurevisite.com/visit/61db0a26-230b-11e9-a6dd-00155d174307" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary">Voir la visite virtuelle </a>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h3>Description du projet :</h3>
        <h4>Un couple de français basé aux USA nous a fait confiance pour leur projet. La division en 2 studios permet de booster la rentabilité  de l'opération  tout en bénéficiant d'une adresse attractive et sécuritaire. Le projet a été très rapide : 4,5 mois entre le premier rendez-vous, la recherche, les travaux ainsi que la mise en location.</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="row text-center logo padded">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icons-bleu-ampoule.svg") %>
            <h5>Objectif</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">Equilibré</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icon-immeuble-bleu.svg") %>
            <h5>Type d’opération</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">Division 2 studios</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("cataneo-icon-rhone.svg") %>
            <h5>Zone</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">Lyon 7 - Saxe Gambetta</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icons-bleu-euro.svg") %>
            <h5>Budget complet</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">243 000 €</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center logo">
          <br>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icon-gain-de-temps.svg") %>
            <h5>Loyers annuels</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">13 200 €</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icon-calculette-bleu.svg") %>
            <h5>Rendement brut</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">7,4%</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("icon-calculette-bleu.svg") %>
            <h5>Rendement net</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">5,3%</h4>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <%= image_tag("cataneo-icon-calendrier.svg") %>
            <h5>Date de l’opération</h5>
            <h4 class="color-blue">11/10/2018</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row text-center padding-top">
      <%= link_to 'Retour aux références', '/references.html', class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    </div>
    <div class="row padding-top text-center">
      <%= link_to 'Lancer mon projet', '/investir.html#response', class: "btn btn-lead-primary" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
